GROUP BY SSTC_3ANT3.EMPLID, SSTC_3ANT3.GPES_YEAR_RECALC, SSTC_3ANT3.GPES_MONTH_RECALC, SSTC_3ANT3.GPES_SSTC_PAYMNT,
